
战士系：擅长使用武器(重武器)作战，使用所有护具。

战士(warrior) ―┬ 骑士(knight) ―┬ 王者(lord)                kni/mag
                │                └ 圣骑士(paladin)           kni/cle
                ├ 勇士(valour) ―┬ 英雄(hero)                war+/mag
                │                └ 超战士(champion)          war++
                ├ 武士(samurai) ―┬ 大名(daimyo)             sam+
                │                 └ 牢人(ronin)              sam/mag
                └ 剑士(swordman) ―┬ 剑术家(fencer)          swd+
                                    └ □兵(mercenary)         swd/mag

  war   - parry, block, disarm, estimate
  kni   - holy bonus, quest bonus
  war+  - two weapons, shield bash
  war++ - power strike, counter attack
  sam   - two weapons, power slash
  sam+  - unholy bonus, critical hit
  swd   - power slash, riposte
  swd+  - counter attack, multiple attack

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
小偷系：擅长闪躲、偷窃、开锁，使用皮革、布类护具。

小偷(thief) ―┬ 强盗(brigand) ―┬ 刽子手(executioner)        asn/war
              │                 └ 杀手(assassin)             asn+
              └ 骗子(trickster) ―┬ 郎中(charlatan)          tri/cle
                                   └ 幻术师(illusionist)      tri/mag

  thi   - dodge, steal, pick lock, hide, sneak
  brg   - plunder, horrify
  asn   - assault, critical
  asn+  - backstab, stealth
  tri   - disguise, charm

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
魔法师系：擅长攻击法术，使用布、魔法类护具。

魔术师(mage) ―┬ 法师(sorcerer) ―┬ 大法师(archmage)         mag++
               │                  └ 贤者(sage)               mag+/cle
               └ 咒术师(conjurer) ―┬ 召唤师(summoner)       sum
                                     └ 魔导士(warlock)        mag+/war

  mag   - scribe, concentrate, magical defense
  mag+  - meditate, spellmaster
  mag++ - forbiden power
  sum   - spellmaster
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
牧师系：擅长辅助、回复法术，使用轻金属、神圣类护具。

牧师(cleric) ―┬ 主教(bishop) ―┬ 大主教(archbishop)         cle++
               │                └ 圣徒(saint)                cle+/mag
               └ 神授战士(crusader) ―┬ 驱魔师(exorcist)     cle+/war
                                       └ 圣者(avatar)         cle/war/mag

  cle   - turn undead, prayer
  cle+  - holy bonus, magical defense, meditate
  cle++ - spellmaster, divine bonus
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
蛮族系：体力、耐力、攻击力高，使用毛皮、石制护具。

蛮族(barbarian) ―┬ 狂战士(berserker) ―┬ 猎头人(headhunter) bar+/war
                  │                     └ 捍卫者(guardian)   bar/war/cle
                  └ 巫医(shaman) ―┬ 降头师(necromancer)     nec
                                    └ 巫毒师(voodooist)       sha/mag

  bar   - melee bonus, berserk, war cry
  bar+  - power strike, assault
  sha   - magical defense, concentrate, spellmaster
  nec   - necromancy
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
士兵系：擅长战术、群体作战、特殊地形作战，使用局部强化护具。

义勇军(militia) ―┬ 士兵(soldier) ―┬ 骑兵(cavalry)          mil+/cav
                  │                 └ 特种部队(combatant)    mil++
                  └ 弓箭手(archer) ―┬ 游骑兵(ranger)        arc/cav
                                      └ 狙击手(sniper)        arc/asn

  mil   - sneak, hide, block, estimate
  mil+  - assault, tactical assist
  mil++ - melee bonus, ambush, raid
  cav   - riding, raid
  arc   - missiles
